 VTuber富士葵离开企业支持，变得“完全独立”、独立（个人） https://p2y.jp/vtuber-fuji-aoi-leaves-corporate-support-and-becomes-completely-independent/ https://p2y.jp/vtuber-fuji-aoi-leaves-corporate-support-and-becomes-completely-independent/#respondp2y_admin Wed, 08 Nov 2023 08:01:35 +0000 VTuberバーチャル音楽LOGIC&MAGIC(ロジックマジック)YouTubeYouTuberバーチャルYouTuberバーチャルシンガーライブ個人勢富士葵https://p2y.jp/?p=105658 <p> VTuber Fuji Aoi 于 2023 年 10 月 7 日（令和 5）离开了 LOGIC &amp; MAGIC Co., Ltd.（附属厂牌：Acro-music）的支持，该公司此前一直在接受支持，并且 […]</p>后<a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-fuji-aoi-leaves-corporate-support-and-becomes-completely-independent/">VTuber Fuji Aoi离开公司支持并成为“完全独立”的独立（个人）</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p> VTuber<strong>富士葵</strong>于 2023 年 10 月 7 日（令和 5 年）发行，离开了此前一直获得支持的 LOGIC &amp; MAGIC Co., Ltd.（附属厂牌：Acro-music）的支持，成为一名独立（个人）人才。宣布将变得“完全独立”。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="105682" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-fuji-aoi-leaves-corporate-support-and-becomes-completely-independent/vtuber_fuji_aoi_leaves_corporate_support_and_becomes_completely_independent/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/vtuber_fuji_aoi_leaves_corporate_support_and_becomes_completely_independent.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="vtuber_fuji_aoi_leaves_corporate_support_and_becomes_completely_independent" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/vtuber_fuji_aoi_leaves_corporate_su